uchte Filmkorpus ein Spannungsfeld zwischen erzählter Invektivität und invektiven Erzählungen.  afunded by Deutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aEmigration and immigration in motion pictures. 0aImmigrants in motion pictures. 0aInvective. 0aMotion pictureszItalyxHistory. 4aEinwanderung. 4aErzählung. 4aGesellschaft. 4aHerabsetzung. 4aImmigration. 4aInvektivität. 4aItalien. 4aKonflikt. 4aKultur. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aMigration. 4aRomanistik. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aConflict.  aCulture.  aDegradation.  aImmigration.  aInvectivity.  aItaly.  aMedia Studies.  aMigration.  aNarrative.  aRomance Studies.  aSociety.2 aDeutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Cultural and Area Studies 2023z978311131812708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2023z9783111024950oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839467121?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839467121423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839467121/original  a978-3-11-131812-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Cultural and Area Studies 2023b2023  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-TGPb2023